&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/USA-NY-BLUE-HILL-AT-STONE-BARNS-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-8021&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/USA-NY-BLUE-HILL-AT-STONE-BARNS-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;USA- NY- BLUE HILL AT STONE BARNS- OFFER LOGO&quot; width=&quot;85&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MEDIA-2016-W50B-LOGO-sized.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-14488&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/MEDIA-2016-W50B-LOGO-sized.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;50Best_2015_logo&quot; width=&quot;50&quot; height=&quot;88&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Blue Hill at Stone Barnes has newly earned a spot&lt;strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;on&nbsp;the&lt;strong&gt;&nbsp;2016 World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants at #48 &lt;/strong&gt;list, as well as winning the &lt;strong&gt;2015 James Beard Award for Outstanding Restaurant&lt;/strong&gt;. Located just forty-five minutes from New York City at Stone Barns Center for Food &amp;amp; Agriculture, once part of the Rockefeller estate, the restaurant features products from local farms and purveyors. Each night an impeccably creative tasting menu is created to highlight the very best of the season. Elegant attire; Jackets and ties are preferred for gentlemen.&lt;br /&gt;
Photo credit: Andre Baranowski&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.bluehillfarm.com/reserve/stone-barns&quot;&gt;book online&lt;/a&gt; or contact Blue Hill at Stone Barns by phone at +1-914-366-9600.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reservations are accepted up to 60 days prior to the calendar date.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Blue Hill at Stone Barns requires a credit card at the time of booking to secure your reservation. Your credit card will not be charged at the time of booking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: If not cancelled 48 hours prior to the dining date or in the event of a no show, a fee in the amount of $100 per guest will be charged to your credit card.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed your reservation may be given away if need arises&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Offer is applicable for the full tasting menu only, not the 3-course bar menu&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating restaurant merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

